just_use flags.go

# label: WORKHORSE
# role: supports feature — read/unread + starred message flags

Two concrete per-(message_id, user_id) tables (unreads, starred_messages)
behind one Zulip-shaped flags API. Semantic flip worth remembering: "add
read" DELETEs from unreads (marking a message read removes its unread row);
"remove read" INSERTs (mark unread). Star is the straightforward
INSERT/DELETE. GetMessageFlags composes both back into the Zulip flags list.
